{
  "stem": "1415.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he got a hold of somebody that told me, and I found my brother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And every once in a while, we used to able to see each other through that back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And one time he told me, I didn't know, but he told me that my mother was in the hospital in that camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, I took it upon myself to go there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I wasn't supposed to leave my-- my barrack, but I did go, and I found my mother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She was sick in that hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my brother [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] He brought some food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because he used to work at Buna, which was the working Auschwitz camp also.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And used to work at the-- air-- I think it was airlines, or whatever they had there, and they were doing something for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he passed me along the electric-- we were so dumb, so crazy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He-- we risked our lives.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The first time he passed me along a little, like, almost the size of a salt shaker.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was a little container that had a cap on it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And it smelled kind of funny inside, but there was salt inside it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And that was, to me, it was like heaven.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Because I used to lick it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So I guess-- I-- I don't know what it did, but it did a lot of good.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I used to lick that salt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And then when he found out that mother was sick, he gave me across one time, like a pudding, A rice pudding or some kind of pudding.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I wanted to eat it so badly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Here was the sentry standing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Here is the electric wires.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
